    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver or a solid base for a restoration project. The exterior shows clear signs of its age, including various scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few small tears, though all essential electronics and controls remain operational. While the car runs and drives, it would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up and some suspension work to return it to peak performance. It is a straightforward, honest car for a buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
