    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine is difficult to start and suffers from several noticeable fluid leaks that require immediate attention. The body and interior also show significant wear and tear, making this a project car for someone willing to invest the necessary time and resources.",
