      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface and mechanical component has been meticulously maintained to ensure an uncompromising driving experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished pedigree and flawless presentation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
